snippet.title: Rusty's Rail - A ToJam13 Game about trains and adventure
snippet.description:
This is a 2 day jam game completed for #ToJam13.
It's sort of a clicker/resource management type game, where you conduct a train, carry passengers to different destinations, and then upgrade your train with the profits made.

A very casual, relaxing, and endless game you can get for free at the following link!
https://welham14.itch.io/rustys-rail


Developers:
Mike Gillespie
Sean Leach
@VanionParadis - Art
Ryan Welham

All assets are our own, except for the music..
Ballade no. 1 in G minor, Op. 23 by Frederic Chopin, as performed by Frank Levy, courtesy of musopen.org under the Public Domain Mark 1.0 license.
